    "Me" "Hm?"

    "Clara" "What are you thinking?"

    "Me" "I'm thinking... maybe we've been overcomplicating this."

    "" "Clara tilted her head."

    "Me" "Eve has already searched every possible hiding spot. If she didn't find it {wait:0.5}"

    "Clara" "Then the letter isn't in any of those places."

    "Me" "Exactly. And the other party knows Eve will search. She even let Eve search willingly."

    "Clara" "Because she knows her hiding spot is somewhere Eve can't find. {change:Clara,preset:body_coat|face=happy}"

    "Me" "Or somewhere Eve would search but wouldn't recognize as a hiding spot."

    actor show Eve neutral at 2
    "" "Eve froze for a moment."

    "Eve" "{change:Eve,surprise}What do you mean?"

